---
title: Cheesy Chicken Parmigiana With Crisp Apple Salad
description: The best part of this chicken parmigiana is the layer of delicious cheese on top! Each bite is juicy, salty and cheesy. Served with a crunchy and refreshing apple salad, dinner tonight is both simple and scrumptious!
